  "title": "NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA",
  "contents": "<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA\", \"name\": \"NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/schema.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L67-L68\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/14.1.0-next.0/packages/core/src/metadata/schema.ts#L67-L68\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"no_errors_schema\">NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA#no_errors_schema\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">定义一个架构，该架构允许任何元素上的任何属性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Defines a schema that allows any property on any element.</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA#description\">查看\"说明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA\" class=\"code-anchor\">NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA</a>: <a href=\"api/core/SchemaMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">SchemaMetadata</a>;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">此模式允许你忽略与模板中任何未知元素或属性相关的错误。通常不鼓励使用此模式，因为它会阻止有用的验证，并且可能会在你的模板中隐藏真正的错误。考虑改用\n<code><a href=\"api/core/CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA\" class=\"code-anchor\">CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA</a></code> 。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">This schema allows you to ignore the errors related to any unknown elements or properties in a\ntemplate. The usage of this schema is generally discouraged because it prevents useful validation\nand may hide real errors in your template. Consider using the <code><a href=\"api/core/CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA\" class=\"code-anchor\">CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA</a></code> instead.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/NgModule\n - api/core/SchemaMetadata\n - guide/testing-components-scenarios\n - guide/upgrade\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA\n - api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA#description\n - api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA#no_errors_schema\n - api/core/SchemaMetadata\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/schema.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L67-L68\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/14.1.0-next.0/packages/core/src/metadata/schema.ts#L67-L68\n-->"
